{"tid":1702391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【東京奧運】主場館掘出逾百副人骨，料屬江戶時代，或設收藏庫助研究","createTime":"2019-11-09T16:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T21:49:08.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2f55ed1c1d80c376579df2b295008be404ddef","tid":1702391,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191109/s00006/18c1acd1095bb3c672560d51f6ad1cdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191109%2Fs00006%2F18c1acd1095bb3c672560d51f6ad1cdc.jpg&h=d5e988d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(明報製圖/Getty Images)<br />\n<br />\n體育<br />\n2019年11月9日星期六<br />\n【東京奧運】主場館掘出逾百副人骨 料屬江戶時代 或設收藏庫助研究 (16:30)<br />\n<br />\n東京奧運主場館「新國立競技場」正在趕工興建，不過當局昨日證實，場館動工前曾挖出187具人骨，估計來自江戶時代，現時由國立科學博物館保存。而日本政府亦計劃增設人骨收藏庫，以助日後研究當時的生活狀况。<br />\n<br />\n明年奧運及殘奧會的主場館位於東京新宿區，鄰近明治神宮外苑；前身國立霞丘陸上競技場於2015年拆除，重建成新國立競技場，預計本月底落成。東京都當局昨日向傳媒透露，在2013至2015年前期勘察時，在競技場及附近地底發現187具人骨，年齡層由嬰兒及至老年人。由於該處於1732至1919年曾是寺廟及墳地，東京都教育委員會估計是江戶時代被埋的屍體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191109/s00006/18c5bcc5f8809dd3cc679df718285c50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191109%2Fs00006%2F18c5bcc5f8809dd3cc679df718285c50.jpg&h=395472fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東京奧運主場館「新國立競技場」於今年7月施工期間。(Getty Images)<br />\n<br />\n而東京都內其他奧運工程現場，至今發現近1000具人骨；專家指這些人骨屬重要研究對象，有助了解當時的生活狀况，盼政府能好好保存。而日本文化廳在明年度預算中，也列入增設人骨收藏庫的項目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20191109/s00006/1573286876010/【東京奧運】主場館掘出逾百副人骨-料屬江戶時代-或設收藏庫助研究\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20191109%2Fs00006%2F1573286876010%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E3%80%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%A0%B4%E9%A4%A8%E6%8E%98%E5%87%BA%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E5%89%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%AA%A8-%E6%96%99%E5%B1%AC%E6%B1%9F%E6%88%B6%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E6%88%96%E8%A8%AD%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%BA%AB%E5%8A%A9%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=7c07d7fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20191109%2Fs00006%2F1573286876010%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E3%80%91%E4%B8%BB%E5%A0%B4%E9%A4%A8%E6%8E%98%E5%87%BA%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E5%89%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%AA%A8-%E6%96%99%E5%B1%AC%E6%B1%9F%E6%88%B6%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E6%88%96%E8%A8%AD%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%BA%AB%E5%8A%A9%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6&h=999e88ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20191109/s00006/1573286876010/【東京奧運】主場館掘出逾百副人骨-料屬江戶時代-或設收藏庫助研究</a>"},{"pid":"41d25063054f70feb7fd20274e803f7cd57254e6","tid":1702391,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:48:36.000Z","msg":"又一個日本仔亂葬崗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae751efe4bba755b593b3310c2d1f3ca8609ff7d","tid":1702391,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41d25063054f70feb7fd20274e803f7cd57254e6","tid":1702391,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T19:48:36.000Z","msg":"又一個日本仔亂葬崗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T21:49:08.000Z","msg":"綠帽兄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}